cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about building medical image classifiers using deep learning techniques, specifically segmentation networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of transfer learning and curriculum learning, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG and cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves training neural networks, which falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with medical imaging, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
